This icy crown grants the wearer resistance to [[cold damage|damage type]]. In addition, you may cast the following spells: [[cone of cold]], [[fire shield]] (chill shield only), [[investiture of ice]]. If you already know any of these spells, casting them using this crown costs one less [[stress]] than normal.